snippet.title: Eiyuden Chronicle: Hundred Heroes - Gameplay Trailer | TGS 2023
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay from Eiyuden Chronicle: Hundred Heroes, the JRPG that puts a modern spin on classic gameplay with 100+ playable characters. Travel and battle through a war-torn world that can only be saved by your collection of specialist heroes.

#IGN #Gaming #EiyudenChronicle
